name: Yu-Gi-Oh
overview:
Yu-Gi-Oh! is presumed to be a backport of one of the Yu-Gi-Oh! game made for the Game Boy Advance, made by Shenzhen Nanjing Technology.

The game is entirely in Chinese, and the fights depend on the dice you roll. The player's monsters cannot go any higher than Level 59, even though the final boss has a monster at Level 60
